org.point85.uom

Enum Unit

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Unit>
      • org.point85.uom.Unit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Unit>

    public enum Unit
extends java.lang.Enum<Unit>
    Unit is an enumeration of common units of measure in the International Customary, SI, US and British Imperial systems.
